### Performance
- **Bundle Size Impact:** +0.5 KB gzipped (just keyboard logic + highlighting)
- **Lazy Loading:** Not needed (code is in modal, already lazy loaded)
- **Optimization:** `highlightText()` memoized per render (React reconciliation handles this)

### Accessibility
- **Keyboard Nav:** ✅ Arrow keys + Enter (standard pattern)
- **Screen Reader:** `aria-selected` on selected widget, `aria-label` on search input
- **Focus Management:** Auto-focus search input when tab opens
- **WCAG AA:** Yellow highlight has sufficient contrast (4.5:1 ratio)

