## Implementation Notes

### Decisions Made
- **2025-11-18** - Use native `<mark>` element instead of `<span>` with yellow background (semantic HTML)
- **2025-11-18** - Auto-focus search input when "Available" tab opens (better UX than requiring click)
- **2025-11-18** - ESC clears search instead of closing modal (modal already has X button)
- **2025-11-18** - Arrow keys wrap around (ArrowDown at end goes to start, ArrowUp at start goes to end) - DECISION: Don't wrap, stay at bounds

### Challenges Anticipated
- **Challenge:** Scrolling selected widget into view when using arrow keys
  - **Solution:** Use `scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' })` on selected widget
  - **Alternative:** Let browser handle scroll naturally

### Deviations from Plan
- None anticipated - straightforward polish features

